OL,3,CNatural Resources Wales to review
OL,4,CStorm Bert weather warnings
OL,6,FWarnings given to residents in Wales
OL,7,Fabout the severity of Storm Bert by
OL,8,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) will be
OL,9,Freviewed in the coming days, an
OL,10,Femployee has said.
OL,12,FA major incident was declared in
OL,13,FRhondda Cynon Taf on Sunday, 24
OL,14,FNovember, with between 200 and 300
OL,15,Fproperties in the area affected by
OL,16,Fflooding from the storm.
OL,18,FCouncil leader Andrew Morgan said the
OL,19,Fweather was worse than forecast and
OL,20,Fthat he was "amazed" only a yellow
OL,21,Fweather warning had been issued.
