OL,6,FWales' First Minister Eluned Morgan
OL,7,Fsaid it had been "a really difficult
OL,8,Fweekend" and was "absolutely
OL,9,Fdevastating just before Christmas" for
OL,10,Fthose affected.
OL,12,FSian Williams, head of operations
OL,13,Fnorth west for NRW, told BBC Radio 4's
OL,14,FToday programme on Monday that the
OL,15,Fagency would look into whether any
OL,16,Fpart of its data gathering for the
OL,17,Fstorm had not been done correctly.
