OL,3,CNatural Resources Wales to review
OL,4,CStorm Bert weather warnings
OL,6,FShe added: "Did something go wrong?
OL,7,FWere the river levels that we use as
OL,8,Ftriggers set in the wrong place? We
OL,9,Fdon't know yet what the timeline was,
OL,10,Fbut it is important that we review it,
OL,11,Fthat we look at it, that we learn
OL,12,Fthose lessons.
OL,14,F"If we need to do it sooner, then
OL,15,Fthat's definitely something that we
OL,16,Fwill look at doing."
OL,18,FTwo severe flood warnings, meaning
OL,19,Fthere is danger to life, have been
OL,20,Fissued for the River Monnow in south-
OL,21,Feast Wales for Monmouth and Skenfrith.
