OL,6,FA further eight flood warnings and 21
OL,7,Fflood alerts also remained in place on
OL,8,FMonday morning.
OL,10,FBut Ms Williams said the worst impacts
OL,11,Fof the storm had now subsided and that
OL,12,Fthe forecast looked "good" over the
OL,13,Fnext couple of days.
OL,15,FShe said: "Thankfully, the river
OL,16,Flevels and the rain has mostly now
OL,17,Fpassed, the river levels are dropping.
