OL,6,F"We do expect now that those flood
OL,7,Fwarnings and alerts will mostly come
OL,8,Fdown today and tomorrow. We believe
OL,9,Fthat the flooding has peaked now in
OL,10,FMonmouthshire, so even on the slower-
OL,11,Frunning rivers on the east of the
OL,12,Fcountry we do expect those levels to
OL,13,Fdrop now."
